<hw>deaf-and-dumb</hw></mhw>
<pos>adj.</pos> <def>both deaf and unable to speak; without the sense of
hearing or the faculty of speech. Same as <er>Deaf-mute</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

